      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"inner strength\" thing... i don't know. it feels like trying to hold onto sand while a storm is hitting. it's just exhausting. everything is so loud and chaotic. when you talk about \"stillness\" or being \"grounded,\" do you mean like... finding a way to actually stop the movement? because sometimes i just want everything to be quiet. really quiet.",
