    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "surfing sounds like so much work though. i don't have the energy to keep fighting the waves or finding a \"rhythm.\" it feels like the only way to actually get some peace is if the ocean just... stopped. if the storm just ended for good. do you think there's a way to find that kind of absolute stillness? like, real stillness where nothing can touch you anymore?",
